Familiar faces at the bash included  Guy Pelly, an old school friend of Princes William and Harry, who is also godfather to her nephew Prince George.

The nightclub owner was escorted by his wife Elizabeth, who teamed her crisp white shirt with an acid lemon skirt.  

Pippa talked and posed for pictures with Andrew Neil, the Chairman of the media group that owns The Spectator.

