This is only Pippa's second outing since returning from the US where she was in talks with the NBC network about a presenting role.

A keen sportswoman, who's currently in training for the 50-mile London to Brighton Bike Ride, she recently stunned in an ice-blue floor length gown at the Disability SnowSport UK Ball.

She met Heather Mills McCartney at the event and gave a speech in which she called for there to be more winter sports opportunities for disabled athletes.

